### Overview
This tool simulatates a water utility warehouse and gives solutions on how to optimize the reorder point.

### Prerequisite
This works on ARENA 2022. it may work on other verions.

### Installation & Setup
download the arena 490_project-update-new.doe file, open, and run

### How to Use
this section gives an overview on how to use the model
# Day creation
This arena model runs every day to check if the season has changed. This is seen at the top, with the create module named "Create day". Seasons are split by 0-89 early winter, 90-284 summer, and 285-365 late winter. and can be adjuted using the decision "Which Season".
